  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You cannot lose concentration on this jutsu as a result of taking damage. You form a massive swell of star chakra that shapes itself into a dragon-like creature composed of pure star chakra in an unoccupied space within range. This dragon is a huge-sized construct. You may dismiss the construct at any time, ending this jutsu</p><p>As part of the action casting this jutsu, you may command the dragon to move up to 60 feet and make up to two attacks at targets within 15 feet of it. On subsequent turns you can command the dragon to move and take the attack action as a bonus action. Otherwise the construct defends itself.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 (or 1 star chakra), the construct's hit points by 2d8 (or +10) and it deals an extra 1d8 damage with its attacks.</p>",
